WEBVTT

00:00.468 --> 00:02.101
<i> PREVIOUSLY</i>
<i> ON "SECRETS AND LIES"...</i>

00:02.102 --> 00:03.735
MY FLASHLIGHT CAME BACK.
GOT TO GET RID OF IT.

00:03.738 --> 00:05.104
IT'S IN A SAFE PLACE.

00:05.106 --> 00:07.306
I CAN'T HELP YOU.
YOU CAN'T AFFORD ME.

00:07.308 --> 00:09.375
THERE'S NO UPSIDE FOR ME
UNTIL YOU GET ARRESTED.

00:09.377 --> 00:11.076
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU DID!

00:11.078 --> 00:12.778
YOU DESTROYED
MY HUSBAND!

00:12.780 --> 00:16.615
I CAN'T. I CAN'T.
I CAN'T!

00:16.617 --> 00:17.616
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

00:17.618 --> 00:19.201
Christy:
A 5-YEAR-OLD IS DEAD.

00:19.202 --> 00:20.785
YOU SLEPT WITH THE WOMAN
ACROSS THE STREET,

00:20.788 --> 00:22.688
AND YOU'RE A SUSPECT
IN A MURDER.

00:22.690 --> 00:23.689
I HATE YOU.

00:23.691 --> 00:26.008
AND I LOVE YOU.

00:26.009 --> 00:28.326
I AM AFTER CORNELL.
AND I NEED YOUR HELP.

00:35.036 --> 00:38.337
CORNELL ONLY WANTS
TO CLOSE HER CASE,

00:38.339 --> 00:41.640
AND SHE WILL DO THAT
ANY WAY SHE CAN.

00:43.344 --> 00:45.677
HELP ME END HER.

00:47.448 --> 00:50.049
NO.

00:53.087 --> 00:55.587
SHE'S GOT THE HIGHEST CLOSE RATE
IN HOMICIDE.

00:55.589 --> 00:57.589
HER STATS
ARE THROUGH THE ROOF.

00:57.591 --> 00:59.608
NOBODY'S THAT GOOD.

00:59.609 --> 01:01.626
AND IF SHE CAN'T FIND EVIDENCE,
SHE MANUFACTURES IT.

01:01.629 --> 01:03.262
I CAN'T BELIEVE
A WORD YOU SAY.

01:03.264 --> 01:04.730
FINE,
THEN DON'T BELIEVE ME.

01:04.732 --> 01:06.765
BUT THERE ARE PLENTY OF PEOPLE
IN PRISON

01:06.767 --> 01:08.801
WHO WOULD TELL YOU
THE EXACT SAME THING.

01:08.803 --> 01:12.204
TAKE, FOR INSTANCE,
JENNIFER BARRETT,
HER LATEST VICTIM.

01:12.206 --> 01:14.706
SHE JUST GOT FRAMED
INTO COUNTY LOCKUP.

01:14.708 --> 01:17.743
AND IF YOU DON'T GET YOUR HEAD
OUT OF YOUR ASS, YOU'RE NEXT.

01:17.745 --> 01:19.745
I'M DONE TRYING TO SOLVE
TOM'S MURDER.

01:19.747 --> 01:22.281
HEY, LOOK, IT'S NOT ABOUT
TRYING TO SOLVE THE CASE.

01:22.283 --> 01:25.851
IF WE CAN GET PROOF
THAT SHE'S ABUSING HER BADGE,

01:25.853 --> 01:28.720
THEN I CAN EXPOSE IT AND YOU
GET THE MONKEY OFF YOUR BACK.

01:28.722 --> 01:31.090
I WOULD NEVER WORK WITH YOU.
GET OUT OF MY WAY.

01:31.092 --> 01:32.357
HEY.

01:32.359 --> 01:35.694
YOU WON'T LIKE PRISON.

01:35.696 --> 01:37.329
WHEN THINGS HAPPEN,

01:37.331 --> 01:41.533
THE GUARDS, THEY PUNISH YOU
BY LOOKING THE OTHER WAY.

01:41.535 --> 01:43.635
YOU DID TIME?

01:43.637 --> 01:47.506
FIVE YEARS AGO,
I GOT TO A MURDER SCENE,

01:47.508 --> 01:50.876
AND THESE YAHOOS,
THEY MISTOOK ME FOR A COP.

01:50.878 --> 01:53.145
CORNELL CHARGED ME
WITH OBSTRUCTION

01:53.147 --> 01:55.647
AND I-IMPERSONATING
AND TAMPERING.

01:55.649 --> 01:57.449
I GOT A FOUR-YEAR BID.

01:57.451 --> 02:00.319
I LOST MY JOB, MY REPUTATION,
AND MY FAMILY.

02:00.321 --> 02:01.587
SOUNDS LIKE
YOU HAD IT COMING.

02:01.589 --> 02:03.455
OTHER REPORTERS
HAVE DONE WORSE

02:03.457 --> 02:05.157
AND GOT A SLAP
ON THE WRIST.

02:05.159 --> 02:09.361
NO. THAT WAS PERSONAL FOR HER,
AND SO IS THIS.

02:09.363 --> 02:11.463
YOU BETTER DO SOMETHING
ABOUT CORNELL,

02:11.465 --> 02:15.801
'CAUSE I GUARANTEE
SHE'S DOING SOMETHING ABOUT<i> YOU.</i>

02:24.211 --> 02:26.545
WHERE'D YOU GO?

02:26.547 --> 02:29.781
I ALMOST
CALLED THE COPS.

02:29.783 --> 02:33.919
THAT REPORTER, ARTHUR FENTON,
HE THREATENED OUR FAMILY.

02:33.921 --> 02:37.456
SO I WENT
TO DEAL WITH IT.

02:37.458 --> 02:39.324
"DEAL WITH IT."

02:39.326 --> 02:41.660
YOU KEEP FIGHTING, BEN.

02:41.662 --> 02:44.496
SHOULD MAKE IT REALLY EASY
FOR CORNELL TO LOCK YOU UP.

02:44.498 --> 02:46.398
IT DOESN'T MATTER
WHAT I DO.

02:46.400 --> 02:48.867
SHE'S NOT GONNA STOP
UNLESS I STOP HER.

02:48.869 --> 02:53.305
HOW ARE<i> YOU</i>
GONNA STOP HER?

02:59.847 --> 03:02.948
[ MAN SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY
ON LOUDSPEAKER ]

03:09.657 --> 03:11.523
I.D.

03:16.297 --> 03:18.330
SIGN IN.

03:18.899 --> 03:22.534
[ BUZZER ]

03:22.536 --> 03:24.203
NOW FACE THE WALL.

03:25.739 --> 03:27.539
[ INDISTINCT TALKING,
DOOR CLANGS ]

03:35.849 --> 03:38.984
ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO.
YOU KNOW THE WAY.

03:40.921 --> 03:43.855
15 MINUTES.
MAKE 'EM COUNT.

03:49.763 --> 03:51.930
[ BUZZER ]

04:05.846 --> 04:09.414
ARE YOU LOOKING FOR METH, TEETH,
AND TATTOOS?

04:09.416 --> 04:12.784
UH, YOU JUST...DON'T SEEM LIKE
THE TYPE THAT BELONGS HERE.

04:12.786 --> 04:14.820
ARE YOU?

04:14.822 --> 04:16.321
NO.

04:16.323 --> 04:18.991
THEN WHY ARE THEY
GIVING YOU THE GLARE?

04:21.295 --> 04:22.828
I HEARD
YOU GOT RAILROADED.

04:22.830 --> 04:24.963
I DON'T WANT THE SAME THING
TO HAPPEN TO ME.

04:26.500 --> 04:28.934
I GUESS
MOM'S BEEN BUSY.

04:28.936 --> 04:31.737
MOM?

04:31.739 --> 04:34.840
DETECTIVE ANDREA CORNELL.

04:42.950 --> 04:46.318
IF ANDREA'S GOT HER HOOKS IN,
YOU GOT TO BE A BADASS.

04:46.320 --> 04:47.853
WHAT'D YOU DO?
NOTHING.

04:47.855 --> 04:50.322
ME TOO.
BUT HERE I AM.

04:50.324 --> 04:53.525
YEAH, FOR DRUGS,
IN CASE YOU'RE WONDERING.

04:53.527 --> 04:54.793
W-WHAT ABOUT REHAB?

04:54.795 --> 04:57.596
MY FATHER ASKED
THE SAME QUESTION.

04:57.598 --> 04:59.965
ANDREA WOULDN'T BUDGE.

04:59.967 --> 05:01.833
THE LAW'S THE LAW.

05:01.835 --> 05:03.702
THERE'S GOT TO BE SOMETHING
YOU CAN DO.

05:03.704 --> 05:05.871
I'M DOING IT.

05:05.873 --> 05:09.541
WITH GOOD BEHAVIOR,
I'M OUT IN 18 MONTHS.

05:11.445 --> 05:13.745
WHAT IS SHE
COMING AFTER YOU FOR?

05:13.747 --> 05:16.815
SHE THINKS
I KILLED A CHILD.

05:16.817 --> 05:20.886
KIND OF SOUNDS LIKE SETH GORING
ALL OVER AGAIN.

05:20.888 --> 05:22.854
WHO'S THAT?

05:22.856 --> 05:26.858
PRIME SUSPECT IN THE MURDER
OF A LITTLE GIRL.

05:26.860 --> 05:29.494
YEAH, THE COPS
COULDN'T PROVE IT,

05:29.496 --> 05:32.531
AND ANDREA STILL CHASES HIM
ON HER DAYS OFF.

05:32.533 --> 05:33.899
IT'S BEEN THREE YEARS.

05:33.901 --> 05:36.068
BUT THAT'S HARASSMENT.

05:36.070 --> 05:39.938
ONCE YOU'RE ON THE WRONG SIDE
OF DETECTIVE CORNELL,

05:39.940 --> 05:42.107
THAT'S WHERE YOU STAY.

05:42.109 --> 05:45.577
CONFESS NOW
AND GET IT OVER WITH.

05:49.683 --> 05:52.851
[ BUZZER ]

05:52.853 --> 05:53.885
MR. CRAWFORD.

05:53.887 --> 05:56.355
SOMEBODY CALLED YOU?

05:56.357 --> 05:58.056
I HAVE A LOT OF FRIENDS.

05:58.058 --> 05:59.725
ENEMIES TOO, I BET.

05:59.727 --> 06:03.061
WHEN A MURDER SUSPECT COMES
AND VISITS MY DAUGHTER,

06:03.063 --> 06:04.963
I TAKE THAT
AS A THREAT.

06:04.965 --> 06:06.631
IS THAT WHAT THIS IS?

06:06.633 --> 06:08.967
I DIDN'T KNOW
SHE WAS YOUR DAUGHTER.

06:08.969 --> 06:11.570
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

06:21.915 --> 06:23.648
Fenton: BEN.
YOU'RE A SNAKE, MAN.

06:23.650 --> 06:24.649
YOU SET ME UP.

06:24.651 --> 06:26.451
OKAY, OKAY, LISTEN.
ALL RIGHT.

06:26.453 --> 06:28.854
CORNELL PUT HER OWN KID
IN PRISON.

06:28.856 --> 06:30.856
I NEEDED YOU TO SEE THAT
FOR YOURSELF

06:30.858 --> 06:32.791
TO REALIZE I WASN'T LYING.

06:32.793 --> 06:34.393
IF I TOLD YOU
WHO JENNIFER REALLY WAS,

06:34.395 --> 06:35.494
THEN YOU WOULDN'T HAVE COME.

06:35.496 --> 06:37.963
SO WHAT DID SHE SAY?
ASK HER YOURSELF.

06:37.965 --> 06:39.798
[ SCOFFS ]
I CAN'T. I'M AN EX-CON.

06:39.800 --> 06:42.067
I'D NEED SPECIAL PERMISSION
TO VISIT A PRISONER.

06:42.069 --> 06:43.635
JUST TELL ME
WHAT SHE SAID.

06:43.637 --> 06:45.904
SHE DIDN'T SAY
A DAMN THING.

06:45.906 --> 06:47.973
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

06:49.877 --> 06:53.478
Jess: I JUST CAN'T TELL YOU
HOW SORRY I AM.

06:53.480 --> 06:55.614
Christy: BEN?

06:55.616 --> 06:57.048
YEAH?

07:05.893 --> 07:06.958
HI.

07:06.960 --> 07:09.127
HI, BEN.

07:10.864 --> 07:14.633
CHRISTY, I NEVER DID
TH-THANK YOU FOR THOSE FLOWERS.

07:14.635 --> 07:15.934
THEY WERE BEAUTIFUL.

07:15.936 --> 07:18.470
TOM WAS
A WONDERFUL BOY.

07:18.472 --> 07:20.839
ALWAYS REMEMBER THAT.

07:26.547 --> 07:28.847
UM, UH, SEE YOU.

07:28.849 --> 07:31.583
MERRY CHRISTMAS.

07:33.754 --> 07:35.587
[ DOOR OPENS ]

07:35.589 --> 07:36.855
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

07:36.857 --> 07:38.890
SHE CAME OVER
TO APOLOGIZE.

07:38.892 --> 07:41.226
I HEARD.

07:41.228 --> 07:43.929
DID YOU
PUT HER UP TO IT?

07:43.931 --> 07:46.498
YES, 'CAUSE IT'S MY DREAM
TO HAVE MY WIFE

07:46.500 --> 07:49.768
AND THE WOMAN I CHEATED WITH
IN THE SAME ROOM, TALKING.

07:49.770 --> 07:51.970
WHERE ARE THE GIRLS?

07:51.972 --> 07:54.739
THE MALL.

07:54.741 --> 07:56.608
HOW ARE YOU DOING?

07:56.610 --> 07:58.910
I'M FINE.

08:00.914 --> 08:02.948
I KNOW WHAT HAPPENED
WITH KEVIN WAS --

08:02.950 --> 08:06.218
SOMETHING I'M WORKING ON.

08:08.989 --> 08:11.957
IT MIGHT HELP YOU
IF YOU TALK ABOUT IT.

08:11.959 --> 08:14.226
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

08:16.797 --> 08:17.896
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

08:17.898 --> 08:19.197
BEN CRAWFORD.

08:21.735 --> 08:24.236
RIGHT NOW?

08:24.238 --> 08:26.605
FINE.

08:26.607 --> 08:29.040
BEN, YOU NEED A LAWYER.

08:29.042 --> 08:32.277
JUST THINK -- WHEN SHE ARRESTS
ME, I'LL GET ONE FOR FREE.

08:43.557 --> 08:44.756
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

08:55.135 --> 08:57.202
Cornell:
SO, YOU HAVE TWO OPTIONS --

08:57.204 --> 09:00.839
CONFESS
AND SPARE YOUR FAMILY

09:00.841 --> 09:03.875
THE HORROR OF A HIGH-PROFILE
MURDER TRIAL...

09:03.877 --> 09:05.677
I DIDN'T KILL TOM.

09:05.679 --> 09:08.914
...OR BRACE YOURSELF
FOR A FULL-COURT PRESS.

09:08.916 --> 09:10.916
'CAUSE THEY'LL NOT ONLY
FOLLOW YOU,

09:10.918 --> 09:13.852
THEY'LL FOLLOW YOUR KIDS,
YOUR WIFE, YOUR KIDS' FRIENDS.

09:13.854 --> 09:15.220
THEY'LL REVEAL
ALL YOUR SECRETS.

09:15.222 --> 09:16.772
WELL, YOU ALREADY DID THAT

09:16.773 --> 09:18.323
WHEN YOU LEAKED THE NEWS
THAT I WAS TOM'S FATHER.

09:18.325 --> 09:20.892
THAT WAS A CRIME-LAB ERROR.
WE'RE LOOKING INTO IT.

09:20.894 --> 09:21.960
AND I BELIEVE YOU.

09:21.962 --> 09:23.662
YOU SHOULD.

09:23.664 --> 09:25.564
I DON'T THINK
YOU HAVE ANY IDEA

09:25.566 --> 09:27.732
THE NIGHTMARE
THAT'S COMING YOUR WAY.

09:27.734 --> 09:28.967
YES, I DO.

09:28.969 --> 09:31.069
I'M LIVING IT.

09:33.173 --> 09:36.041
THIS IS ABOUT
YOUR DAUGHTER.

09:36.043 --> 09:39.844
THIS IS ABOUT
THE DEAD 5-YEAR-OLD

09:39.846 --> 09:41.179
THAT YOU FOUND
IN THE WOODS.

09:41.181 --> 09:43.748
YOU CAN'T TELL ME
THAT THIS DISPLAY,

09:43.750 --> 09:46.651
ALL OF THIS,
ISN'T PERSONAL.

09:46.653 --> 09:50.121
I THINK YOU'RE BEING PARANOID,
AND THAT'S A SYMPTOM OF PTSD.

09:50.123 --> 09:52.791
YOU SHOULD REALLY
GET HELP FOR THAT.

09:53.894 --> 09:55.994
THERE'S A THIRD OPTION
YOU DIDN'T CONSIDER.

09:55.996 --> 09:58.196
WHAT'S THAT?

09:58.198 --> 10:02.767
I CAN GO HOME,
AND YOU CAN GO TO HELL.

10:02.769 --> 10:04.069
HOW'S THAT?

10:13.747 --> 10:16.781
COLORS?
WHAT ABOUT THE WHITE SNEAKERS?
THEY'RE TOO TIGHT.

10:16.783 --> 10:19.751
YOU'VE GOT TO
STOP GROWING.

10:22.789 --> 10:23.989
HI, DAD.

10:23.991 --> 10:25.657
HEY, MONKEY.

10:25.659 --> 10:27.225
WHERE'S MY HUG?

10:27.227 --> 10:29.661
MOM SAID
I SHOULDN'T HUG YOU.

10:29.663 --> 10:31.930
I SAID TO WAIT FOR YOUR DAD
TO HUG YOU FIRST.

10:33.300 --> 10:35.367
HOW'D I BECOME
THE BAD GUY?

10:35.369 --> 10:37.669
'CAUSE YOU'RE
SO GOOD AT IT.

10:39.973 --> 10:41.873
MICHAEL HAS INVITED
A LOT OF NEW PEOPLE

10:41.875 --> 10:43.742
TO HIS CHRISTMAS PARTY
THIS YEAR.

10:43.744 --> 10:45.710
PLENTY OF KIDS YOUR AGE.
IT SHOULD BE FUN.

10:45.712 --> 10:47.045
HIS PARTIES ARE LAME.

10:47.047 --> 10:49.614
W--

10:49.615 --> 10:52.182
GAY PEOPLE ARE SUPPOSED TO BE,
WELL, GAY, AREN'T THEY?

10:52.185 --> 10:52.951
NATALIE!

10:52.953 --> 10:55.487
NATALIE,

10:55.488 --> 10:58.022
GAY PEOPLE CAN BE JUST AS BORING
AS EVERYBODY ELSE.

11:02.729 --> 11:04.029
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

11:04.031 --> 11:05.714
WHERE YOU BEEN, MAN?

11:05.715 --> 11:07.398
I GETTING THE CHILL FROM
FROSTY THE SNOW LADY IN THERE.

11:07.401 --> 11:12.170
CORNELL BROUGHT ME IN,
SHOWED ME ALL THE EVIDENCE.

11:12.172 --> 11:14.205
SHE HAD A FLASHLIGHT
FRONT AND CENTER.

11:14.207 --> 11:16.041
IT'S EXACTLY LIKE MINE.

11:16.043 --> 11:18.977
OH, NO.

11:18.978 --> 11:21.912
YEAH, MAN. IT MADE ME ANXIOUS
TO GET RID OF IT.

11:21.915 --> 11:24.816
OKAY.

11:24.818 --> 11:26.685
DID YOU PICK A HIDING SPOT?

11:26.687 --> 11:29.754
I'M THINKING BACK BEHIND
THE ARGYLE MALL, LIKE YOU SAID,

11:29.756 --> 11:32.257
ON THE WAY TO MICHAEL'S
AND IN THE WOODS THERE.

11:32.259 --> 11:35.326
CORNELL MUST HAVE
REALLY SPOOKED YOU.

11:35.328 --> 11:37.128
WHAT I HEAR ABOUT HER,

11:37.130 --> 11:39.998
I'M GOING TO PRISON
WHETHER I DID IT OR NOT.

11:40.000 --> 11:42.267
HEAR FROM WHO?

11:42.269 --> 11:44.135
CORNELL'S DAUGHTER.

11:44.137 --> 11:45.904
YOU'RE TALKING
TO THE COP'S FAMILIES NOW?

11:45.906 --> 11:47.305
WHAT,
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?

11:47.307 --> 11:48.907
MAN, IF I'M GONNA
GET OUT OF THIS,

11:48.909 --> 11:50.842
I GOT TO PROVE
THAT CORNELL'S CROOKED.

11:50.844 --> 11:52.744
OKAY. I GET YOU. HOW?

11:52.746 --> 11:55.814
I'M GONNA TRACK DOWN THIS
OTHER GUY SHE'S BEEN CHASING

11:55.816 --> 11:57.616
AND COMPARE NOTES.

11:57.617 --> 11:59.417
TAKE THE SECRET FILES
TO THE GOVERNMENT.

11:59.419 --> 12:00.885
IT'S A GOOD PLAN.

12:00.887 --> 12:02.821
THE PRESS.
DON'T TELL ME.

12:02.823 --> 12:05.023
THE REPORTER WHO OUTED THE DOC
AND HIS SISTER --

12:05.025 --> 12:06.491
OH, WAIT,
I MEAN HIS WIFE?

12:06.493 --> 12:08.126
THAT GUY SHEDS HIS SKIN,
MAN.

12:08.128 --> 12:09.794
YOU DON'T -- YOU DON'T WANT
TO DEAL WITH THAT GUY.

12:09.796 --> 12:12.430
I DON'T NEED TO TRUST FENTON
TO USE HIM.

12:35.021 --> 12:35.887
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

12:35.889 --> 12:37.355
Ben: HELLO?

12:37.357 --> 12:40.225
UH, WHO ARE YOU?

12:40.227 --> 12:43.061
MY NAME'S BEN CRAWFORD.
I'M LOOKING FOR SETH GORING.

12:43.063 --> 12:44.829
AM I IN THE RIGHT PLACE?

12:44.831 --> 12:45.897
UH...

12:45.899 --> 12:48.032
MOM?

12:51.004 --> 12:54.839
I KNOW YOU.
FROM THE NEWS.

12:54.841 --> 12:56.040
YEAH, I'VE SEEN YOU BEFORE.

12:56.042 --> 12:58.109
YOU WERE AT THE --
THE POLICE STATION,

12:58.111 --> 12:59.811
YELLING AT DETECTIVE CORNELL.

12:59.813 --> 13:03.047
CAN I COME IN?

13:03.049 --> 13:04.816
MOM,
DON'T TALK TO THIS GUY.

13:04.818 --> 13:06.417
STAY OUT OF IT, JIMMY.

13:06.419 --> 13:09.087
IT'S OKAY.

13:12.292 --> 13:13.958
WE'RE GONNA GO PACK
OUR ROOMS.

13:13.960 --> 13:15.026
OKAY.

13:21.234 --> 13:23.935
MY BOYS
HAVE BEEN THROUGH A LOT.

13:23.937 --> 13:25.203
BECAUSE OF CORNELL.

13:25.205 --> 13:28.406
YEAH.
YOU MUST KNOW ALL ABOUT THAT.

13:28.408 --> 13:30.241
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.

13:30.243 --> 13:34.078
I...WANTED TO ASK YOUR HUSBAND
WHAT SHE DID TO HIM.

13:39.853 --> 13:43.021
A LITTLE GIRL
WAS STRANGLED.

13:43.023 --> 13:46.958
CORNELL CLAIMED MY HUSBAND
HAD COMPULSIONS

13:46.960 --> 13:49.928
AND THAT OTHER GIRLS
CAME FORWARD, AS WELL.

13:49.930 --> 13:52.163
ALL LIES.

13:52.165 --> 13:56.100
I MEAN, IF IT WERE TRUE,
SETH WOULD'VE BEEN ARRESTED.

13:56.102 --> 13:58.002
BUT CORNELL
KEPT COMING BACK.

13:58.004 --> 14:01.005
SHE WOULDN'T LET GO.

14:01.006 --> 14:04.007
EVERY TIME WE MOVED,
SHE'D QUESTION OUR NEIGHBORS.

14:04.010 --> 14:06.978
HAD SETH BEEN SEEN
WITH ANY LITTLE GIRLS?

14:06.980 --> 14:09.948
YOU CAN JUST IMAGINE
WHAT SHE MADE THEM THINK

14:09.950 --> 14:12.851
ABOUT MY HUSBAND
AND ABOUT US.

14:12.853 --> 14:13.985
I'M SORRY.

14:13.987 --> 14:16.538
I'M SORRY, TOO.

14:16.539 --> 14:19.090
YOU HAVE NO IDEA HOW MUCH WORSE
THIS IS GOING TO GET.

14:19.092 --> 14:21.292
ISN'T THERE ANYTHING
YOU CAN DO ABOUT HER?

14:21.294 --> 14:25.096
LIKE LODGE A COMPLAINT,
CALL ONE OF HER SUPERVISORS?

14:25.098 --> 14:29.534
WE TRIED, BUT NOW THERE'S
NOTHING LEFT TO FIGHT FOR.

14:29.536 --> 14:31.403
WHY NOT?

14:31.404 --> 14:33.271
[ Voice breaking ] MY HUSBAND
JUST COULDN'T TAKE IT ANYMORE.

14:33.273 --> 14:34.539
[ SNIFFLES ]

14:34.541 --> 14:37.508
I FOUND HIM IN THE BASEMENT.

14:37.510 --> 14:39.644
HUNG HIMSELF A WEEK AGO.

14:44.451 --> 14:47.085
CORNELL HOUNDED THE GUY
TO DEATH. HOW IS THAT LEGAL?

14:47.087 --> 14:48.453
HOW CAN SHE GET AWAY WITH --
NO, EXACTLY.

14:48.455 --> 14:49.988
AS LONG AS THERE'S
AN OPEN MURDER,

14:49.990 --> 14:51.122
SHE CAN DO
WHATEVER SHE WANTS TO.

14:51.124 --> 14:53.091
I CAN'T GO ON LIKE THIS
FOR YEARS.

14:53.093 --> 14:54.359
WELL, ONCE I WRITE ABOUT

14:54.361 --> 14:56.461
WHAT SETH GORING WENT THROUGH
AT HER HANDS,

14:56.463 --> 14:58.263
YOU WON'T HAVE TO.

14:58.265 --> 14:59.631
YOU GOT TO GO.

14:59.633 --> 15:01.232
I JUST GOT HERE.

15:01.234 --> 15:02.967
YEAH, UNANNOUNCED,
AND I HAVE AN APPOINTMENT.

15:02.969 --> 15:04.335
CORNELL RUINED YOUR LIFE.
WHAT'S MORE IMPORTANT THAN THAT?

15:04.337 --> 15:05.937
SERIOUSLY.
YOU GOT TO GO.

15:05.939 --> 15:07.038
YOU ASKED FOR INFORMATION.
COME ON.

15:07.040 --> 15:08.406
YEAH. I'LL CALL YOU.

15:09.943 --> 15:11.609
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

15:32.198 --> 15:35.133
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

15:45.378 --> 15:47.679
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

15:49.215 --> 15:50.281
[ BEEP, VIBRATING STOPS ]

15:58.191 --> 15:59.724
HEY, IS, UH --
IS FENTON HOME?

15:59.726 --> 16:03.661
UH, YEAH, HE'S --
HE'S IN BACK.

16:03.663 --> 16:04.495
NAME'S BEN.

16:04.497 --> 16:06.064
LINDA.

16:11.037 --> 16:12.537
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

16:19.212 --> 16:22.280
[ SIGHS ] MOM'S ABOUT TO
SEND OUT A SEARCH PARTY.

16:22.282 --> 16:24.115
WHY? WHAT'S THE RUSH?

16:24.117 --> 16:25.700
TWO MORE DAYS
TILL CHRISTMAS!
DORK.

16:25.701 --> 16:27.284
Christy: I'VE BEEN CALLING.
WE NEED TO GET ON THE ROAD.

16:27.287 --> 16:28.586
WHERE'D YOU GO?

16:28.588 --> 16:30.355
ERRANDS.

16:30.357 --> 16:31.723
WELL, HURRY UP.
WE'RE GONNA BE LATE.

16:31.725 --> 16:32.991
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

16:38.732 --> 16:41.532
ALL RIGHT.

16:54.681 --> 16:56.314
OH!
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

16:56.316 --> 16:58.282
Ben:
WHOSE GIFT WAS THAT?

16:58.284 --> 16:59.751
MICHAEL'S.

16:59.753 --> 17:01.652
I GUESS I KNOW
WHAT IT IS.

17:01.654 --> 17:03.488
IT WAS MY FAULT.

17:03.490 --> 17:05.089
HONEY, IT WASN'T YOUR FAULT.
I DROPPED IT.

17:05.091 --> 17:06.758
WE'LL STOP AND PICK UP SOMETHING
ON THE WAY.

17:06.760 --> 17:08.726
FORGET IT. JUST --
I DON'T WANT TO FORGET IT.

17:08.728 --> 17:10.561
THINGS ARE TENSE ENOUGH
ALREADY.

17:10.563 --> 17:12.730
LET'S NOT MAKE IT WORSE.

17:12.732 --> 17:15.033
THERE'S GONNA BE NOWHERE
TO PARK.

17:15.035 --> 17:17.168
YOU GUYS RUN IN,
AND I'LL JUST CIRCLE.

17:17.170 --> 17:19.504
Christy: WHY IS THIS
SO IMPORTANT TO YOU?

17:19.506 --> 17:21.406
AFTER WHAT
I JUST WENT THROUGH,

17:21.408 --> 17:24.509
I-I JUST --

17:24.511 --> 17:26.744
I WANT NORMAL RIGHT NOW.

17:26.746 --> 17:29.113
WE'LL FIND SOMETHING.

17:29.115 --> 17:29.814
YEAH?
YEAH.

17:29.816 --> 17:31.416
YEAH.

17:31.418 --> 17:34.152
ALL RIGHT,
LET ME PULL UP HERE.

17:35.755 --> 17:37.088
COME ON.

17:37.090 --> 17:38.456
I WANT TO STAY WITH DAD.

17:39.759 --> 17:41.259
COME HERE.

17:42.162 --> 17:45.063
GET MOM TO KEEP IT
UNDER 50 BUCKS, OKAY?

17:45.065 --> 17:47.231
I'M ON IT.
ALL RIGHT.

17:52.372 --> 17:54.405
[ HORN HONKS ]

18:23.103 --> 18:25.169
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

19:12.852 --> 19:15.219
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

19:17.357 --> 19:18.890
WHERE WERE YOU?

19:18.892 --> 19:21.159
I HAD TO TAKE A LEAK.

19:21.161 --> 19:23.327
WHERE'S THE GIRLS?

19:23.329 --> 19:25.229
THEY'RE WAITING.

19:26.866 --> 19:28.166
LET'S GO GET THEM.

19:31.371 --> 19:32.837
DID YOU FIND ANYTHING?

19:32.839 --> 19:36.741
YEAH.
ABBY PICKED IT OUT.

19:36.743 --> 19:38.342
[ SEAT BELT CLICKS ]

19:38.344 --> 19:39.911
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

19:46.819 --> 19:49.720
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

19:53.660 --> 19:56.561
ALL RIGHT, GIRLS, HELP US
UNPACK, AND THEN I'LL GO PARK.

19:57.897 --> 19:59.497
HEY, GUYS.
COMING DOWN TO HELP.

19:59.499 --> 20:00.865
WE'VE GOT IT COVERED.
HEY, UNCLE MICHAEL!

20:00.867 --> 20:02.934
MERRY CHRISTMAS,
UNCLE MICHAEL!
LOOKS AMAZING.

20:02.936 --> 20:04.969
Michael:
SLIPPERY, GUYS. BE CAREFUL.

20:04.971 --> 20:07.838
NATALIE,
JUST RIGHT UPSTAIRS.

20:09.676 --> 20:10.908
BEN, HOW ARE YOU?

20:10.910 --> 20:12.777
GETTING BETTER
EVERY DAY.

20:12.779 --> 20:14.579
THERE SHOULD BE
ANOTHER PRESENT, DAD.

20:14.581 --> 20:16.681
WELL,
THAT'S ALL THERE IS.

20:16.683 --> 20:19.617
BUT I COUNTED.
THERE HAS TO BE ONE MORE.

20:19.619 --> 20:22.420
ABBY, GO INSIDE
WITH YOUR UNCLE.

20:23.923 --> 20:26.257
COME ON, NOW. GO.

20:26.259 --> 20:28.259
Michael: THANK YOU.

20:28.261 --> 20:30.628
RIGHT BEHIND YOU,
SWEETHEART.

20:34.867 --> 20:36.500
WHAT'S GOING ON?

20:36.502 --> 20:37.702
WHAT?

20:37.704 --> 20:40.538
I KNOW YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH
AN AWFUL ORDEAL,

20:40.540 --> 20:42.840
BUT I AM TIRED
OF WALKING ON EGGSHELLS.

20:42.842 --> 20:45.743
I DIDN'T ASK YOU TO.

20:45.745 --> 20:47.979
WHAT WERE YOU DOING
IN THE WOODS?

20:47.981 --> 20:49.847
I TOLD YOU
WHAT I WAS DOING.

20:52.285 --> 20:53.951
YOU'RE LYING TO ME.

20:53.953 --> 20:55.586
[ SCOFFS ]

20:55.588 --> 20:57.738
WHY WOULD I LIE
ABOUT THAT?

20:57.739 --> 20:59.889
I DON'T KNOW, BUT ABBY COUNTED
THE PRESENTS BEFORE WE LEFT.

20:59.892 --> 21:02.927
NOW THERE'S ONE MISSING.
EXPLAIN THAT.

21:02.929 --> 21:06.530
I CAN'T.

21:06.532 --> 21:09.300
WHAT'S IN
THE BACKPACK, BEN?

21:09.302 --> 21:11.636
CHRISTMAS STUFF.

21:11.638 --> 21:13.404
IF YOU'RE NOT GONNA TELL ME,

21:13.406 --> 21:15.873
THEN MICHAEL
CAN DRIVE US HOME LATER.

21:15.875 --> 21:17.942
YOU SHOULD GO.

21:17.944 --> 21:20.278
GOOD IDEA.

21:24.284 --> 21:25.816
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

21:25.818 --> 21:28.019
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

21:37.297 --> 21:39.930
[ ENGINE REVS ]

21:44.771 --> 21:47.305
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

21:47.307 --> 21:49.573
[ HORN HONKING ]

21:49.575 --> 21:51.776
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

21:53.780 --> 21:55.313
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

21:55.315 --> 21:56.814
[ HORN HONKS ]

22:00.787 --> 22:02.520
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

22:02.522 --> 22:03.654
[ ENGINE REVS ]

22:08.928 --> 22:11.562
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

22:11.831 --> 22:13.664
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

22:17.003 --> 22:18.836
[ ENGINE REVS ]

22:18.838 --> 22:19.837
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

22:19.839 --> 22:21.005
[ HORN HONKS ]

22:21.007 --> 22:23.407
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

22:25.445 --> 22:26.877
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

22:26.879 --> 22:28.813
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

22:28.815 --> 22:30.881
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

22:36.556 --> 22:39.390
Man:
LET ME SEE YOUR HANDS!

22:41.794 --> 22:44.528
EYES FORWARD.

22:47.900 --> 22:50.534
WHY'D WE PULL YOU OVER?

22:50.536 --> 22:52.803
I DON'T KNOW, OFFICER.
I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING WRONG.

22:52.805 --> 22:57.541
YEAH, YOU DID.
WHY'D WE PULL YOU OVER?

22:57.543 --> 23:00.144
CORNELL'S DAUGHTER?

23:00.146 --> 23:02.947
YOU DON'T SCREW
WITH A COP'S FAMILY.

23:02.949 --> 23:06.050
ANY MORE DUMBASS MOVES,
AND YOU COULD DISAPPEAR.

23:25.905 --> 23:27.938
[ BREATHING SHAKILY ]

23:32.912 --> 23:35.179
[ COUGHING ]

23:35.181 --> 23:38.015
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

23:44.991 --> 23:46.524
[ WATER SPLASHES ]

23:52.498 --> 23:53.864
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

23:58.771 --> 24:01.806
MEET ME AT MY HOUSE -- NOW.

24:01.808 --> 24:03.808
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

24:03.810 --> 24:05.343
Ben:
THIS WAS A DIRECT THREAT!

24:05.344 --> 24:06.877
IT'S PROOF THAT CORNELL'S
ABUSING HER BADGE!

24:06.879 --> 24:08.779
Fenton:
NO, NOT EVEN CLOSE.

24:08.781 --> 24:11.449
YOU CAN'T PICK THEM
OUT OF A LINEUP, NO PLATES.

24:11.451 --> 24:13.517
YOU CAN'T EVEN DESCRIBE
THEIR CARS.

24:13.519 --> 24:15.519
ALL RIGHT, WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO
ABOUT CORNELL?

24:15.521 --> 24:16.587
[ SIGHS ]

24:17.490 --> 24:21.892
WELL, THE GORING ARTICLE
IS GAINING TRACTION.

24:21.894 --> 24:24.595
A.P. JUST PICKED IT UP.

24:24.597 --> 24:25.529
MM?

24:25.531 --> 24:26.864
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:26.866 --> 24:29.133
THANKS, PARTNER.
I'LL TALK TO YOU SOON.

24:36.776 --> 24:38.542
HEY, MAN.

24:38.544 --> 24:41.178
YOU KNOW, YOU GOT A REAL SKUNK
PROBLEM ON YOUR FRONT PORCH.

24:41.180 --> 24:44.014
FENTON'S NOT MY PROBLEM.
I GOT HIM UNDER CONTROL.

24:44.016 --> 24:46.650
BUT IF YOU DON'T STOP
BREAKING AND ENTERING --

24:46.652 --> 24:47.818
I USED THE KEY
THAT YOU GAVE ME.

24:47.820 --> 24:49.253
I KNEW YOU WEREN'T
GONNA BE HERE.

24:49.255 --> 24:50.721
WHERE'S THE BROOD?

24:50.723 --> 24:52.823
STILL AT MICHAEL'S.

24:52.825 --> 24:57.161
HOW DID THE, UH,
FLASHLIGHT DITCH GO?

24:57.163 --> 24:59.063
I WRAPPED IT UP LIKE A GIFT

24:59.065 --> 25:02.633
AND CARRIED IT OUT
WITH THE REST OF THE PRESENTS.

25:02.635 --> 25:03.767
THAT'S GENIUS.

25:04.737 --> 25:06.237
OUT BY THE MALL?
Ben: YEAH.

25:06.239 --> 25:08.172
I DON'T FEEL GOOD ABOUT IT,

25:08.174 --> 25:11.876
BUT I PUT IT BACK BEHIND
THOSE THICK TREES, YOU KNOW?

25:11.878 --> 25:13.177
OKAY. GOOD MAN.

25:13.179 --> 25:16.247
ALMOST BROKE MY LEG
ON A SHOPPING CART.

25:16.249 --> 25:17.948
IT'S DONE.
IT'S DONE.

25:17.950 --> 25:20.985
AND THEN CHRISTY WAS STANDING
THERE WAITING WHEN I CAME BACK.

25:20.987 --> 25:22.920
SO WHAT?
YOU WERE TAKING A LEAK, RIGHT?

25:22.922 --> 25:24.622
THAT'S WHAT I SAID, BUT --

25:24.624 --> 25:25.756
SHE DOESN'T KNOW ANYTHING,
RIGHT?

25:25.758 --> 25:27.224
DOES SHE KNOW ANYTHING?

25:28.928 --> 25:31.228
BEN?

25:31.230 --> 25:32.963
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

25:40.673 --> 25:42.990
YOU LYING BITCH.

25:42.991 --> 25:45.308
YOU KNOW, MY MOM FELT SORRY
FOR YOU, AND YOU SCREWED US.

25:45.311 --> 25:46.744
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

25:46.746 --> 25:48.429
YOU TALKED TO THE PRESS
ABOUT MY DAD,

25:48.430 --> 25:50.113
AND NOW IT'S
STARTING ALL OVER AGAIN.
I DIDN'T SCREW YOU.

25:50.116 --> 25:52.082
NOW EVERYBODY KNOWS
YOUR FATHER WAS INNOCENT

25:52.084 --> 25:53.918
AND CORNELL'S RESPONSIBLE
FOR HIS DEATH.

25:53.920 --> 25:54.952
NO, SHE'S NOT!

25:54.954 --> 25:56.153
SHE RUINED
YOUR FAMILY'S LIVES!

25:56.155 --> 25:59.290
NO, MY FATHER WAS GUILTY,
OKAY?

25:59.292 --> 26:02.693
HE RAPED THAT GIRL, AND THEN
HE STRANGLED HER TO DEATH!

26:04.997 --> 26:06.297
HOW DO YOU KNOW?

26:06.299 --> 26:10.067
I FOUND PHOTOS
STASHED IN THE BASEMENT.

26:10.069 --> 26:12.202
AND THEN I SHOWED HIM
THE PICTURES.

26:13.873 --> 26:15.940
AND THEN HE...

26:17.310 --> 26:19.310
[ SIGHS ]
THAT'S AWFUL, MAN.

26:19.312 --> 26:20.978
[ SNIFFLES ]

26:20.979 --> 26:22.645
MY MOTHER DIDN'T KNOW
THAT HE WAS GUILTY,

26:22.648 --> 26:24.048
BUT NOW, WITH THE ARTICLE,

26:24.050 --> 26:27.117
THE COPS ARE GONNA
START DIGGING AGAIN, AND SHE --

26:27.119 --> 26:28.919
SHE --

26:41.867 --> 26:44.101
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

26:45.738 --> 26:49.106
HEY. WHAT ARE YOU
DOING UP SO EARLY?

26:49.108 --> 26:51.909
I WANTED TO TALK TO YOU.

26:55.648 --> 26:58.749
YESTERDAY,
UH...YOUR MOM AND --

26:58.751 --> 27:01.118
YOU AND MOM HAD A FIGHT.

27:01.120 --> 27:03.320
ONE OF MANY.

27:05.858 --> 27:07.891
IT MADE ME THINK.

27:07.893 --> 27:09.259
ABOUT WHAT?

27:13.232 --> 27:17.234
MOST OF MY FRIENDS HAVE PROBLEMS
WITH THEIR MOTHERS --

27:17.236 --> 27:23.107
WITH, UM, MAKEUP,
BOYS, CLOTHES...

27:23.109 --> 27:24.908
BOYS, SEX, BOYS.

27:24.910 --> 27:27.678
YEAH, I HAVE PROBLEMS
WITH THOSE THINGS, TOO.

27:27.680 --> 27:29.046
YEAH.

27:29.048 --> 27:32.316
BUT MOM'S
EASIER TO DEAL WITH.

27:32.318 --> 27:36.020
I THINK SHE'S TRYING TOO HARD
NOT TO BE LIKE NANA.

27:36.022 --> 27:41.325
YOU'RE ON ME ABOUT
PRETTY MUCH EVERYTHING,

27:41.327 --> 27:43.994
AND I HATE IT.

27:47.133 --> 27:50.134
BUT I...

27:50.136 --> 27:54.238
ALSO KIND OF KNOW
THAT I NEED THAT.

27:56.409 --> 27:59.209
SO WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

27:59.211 --> 28:02.012
WELL...

28:02.014 --> 28:05.949
[ Voice breaking ]
WHAT DO I DO...

28:05.951 --> 28:10.721
IF YOU...GO AWAY?

28:10.723 --> 28:13.090
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

28:13.092 --> 28:16.093
WHERE'S ABBY?

28:16.095 --> 28:18.462
Abby: WHY WON'T YOU
LEAVE MY FATHER ALONE?!
Cornell: ABBY.

28:18.464 --> 28:20.330
HE DIDN'T KILL TOM!
WHY WON'T YOU BELIEVE HIM?!

28:20.332 --> 28:22.299
ABBY,
I NEED YOU TO CALM DOWN.
HE DIDN'T DO ANYTHING WRONG!

28:22.301 --> 28:23.934
YOU'RE RUINING EVERYTHING!
ABBY. STOP IT!

28:23.936 --> 28:25.903
IT'S ALL YOUR FAULT!
WHY DO YOU KEEP COMING HERE?

28:25.904 --> 28:27.871
IT'D PROBABLY BE BEST
IF YOU TAKE YOUR FAMILY INSIDE.
HE DIDN'T DO ANYTHING WRONG!

28:27.873 --> 28:28.972
Christy: ABBY, STOP.

28:28.974 --> 28:30.974
WE CAN'T LEAVE DAD ALONE
WITH HER.

28:30.976 --> 28:33.010
HONEY, IT'S OKAY.
YOU GUYS GO IN.

28:39.351 --> 28:41.485
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

28:41.487 --> 28:44.088
ANYTHING YOU SAY CAN AND WILL
BE USED AGAINST YOU.

28:44.090 --> 28:45.856
DO YOU UNDERSTAND,
MR. CRAWFORD?

28:45.858 --> 28:47.491
AM I UNDER ARREST?

28:47.493 --> 28:50.794
YOU CAN CALL AN ATTORNEY
AND TELL HIM WHERE TO MEET US.

28:50.796 --> 28:52.496
WHERE ARE WE GOING?

28:57.970 --> 29:00.137
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS,
POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

29:05.111 --> 29:06.443
[ CAR DOORS CLOSE ]

29:06.445 --> 29:08.879
Man: MR. CRAWFORD.
THIS WAY.

29:22.361 --> 29:24.094
BEGIN.

29:24.096 --> 29:25.929
Man: ALL RIGHT,
YOU HEARD HER.

29:25.931 --> 29:28.332
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

30:16.415 --> 30:18.549
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

30:18.551 --> 30:20.017
WHY ARE WE HERE?

30:20.019 --> 30:22.219
YOU TOLD ME TO CALL YOU
AS SOON AS I WAS ARRESTED.

30:22.221 --> 30:24.087
IF YOU WERE,
YOU'D BE IN CUFFS.

30:24.089 --> 30:26.590
IT'S CALLED
CUSTODIAL INTERROGATION.

30:26.592 --> 30:29.526
A BUSH-LEAGUE
INTIMIDATION TACTIC, BY THE WAY.

30:29.528 --> 30:32.095
IT'S ONLY EFFECTIVE
IF YOU SPEAK.

30:32.097 --> 30:33.564
DID YOU?
NO.

30:33.566 --> 30:35.966
JOHN,
I STILL CAN'T PAY YOU.

30:35.968 --> 30:37.901
I GOT A CASHIER'S CHECK
FOR 25 GRAND

30:37.903 --> 30:39.970
WITH YOUR NAME ON IT
LAST WEEK.

30:39.972 --> 30:41.405
I DON'T HAVE
THAT KIND OF MONEY.

30:41.407 --> 30:42.906
ALL RIGHT,
WE'LL DEAL WITH THAT LATER.

30:42.908 --> 30:44.174
I STILL WANT TO KNOW
WHY WE'RE HERE.

30:44.176 --> 30:45.075
ASK CORNELL.

30:45.077 --> 30:47.061
NO, I'M ASKING YOU.

30:47.062 --> 30:49.046
NO COP BRINGS A FULL
CRIME-SCENE UNIT TO THE BOONIES

30:49.048 --> 30:51.031
FOR NO REASON.

30:51.032 --> 30:53.015
ALL RIGHT, I STOPPED HERE
LAST NIGHT WITH MY FAMILY.

30:53.018 --> 30:55.185
I WENT INTO THE WOODS
TO TAKE A LEAK.

30:55.187 --> 30:57.187
END OF STORY.

30:57.189 --> 30:59.022
CORNELL MUST BE
WORKING OFF A TIP

30:59.024 --> 31:00.390
THAT YOU
THREW AWAY EVIDENCE.

31:00.392 --> 31:03.927
DID ANYONE SEE YOU
RELIEVING YOURSELF?

31:03.929 --> 31:05.062
JUST MY WIFE.

31:06.198 --> 31:09.032
I GUESS
CHRISTY CALLED CORNELL.

31:09.034 --> 31:10.534
NO, NO, NO, NO.

31:10.535 --> 31:12.035
COMMUNICATION BETWEEN A HUSBAND
AND WIFE IS PRIVILEGED.

31:12.037 --> 31:14.037
CORNELL WOULD NEVER ACT
ON A BAD LEAD.

31:14.039 --> 31:15.639
MR. GARNER.

31:15.641 --> 31:17.341
DETECTIVE,
NEXT TIME YOU WANT TO FISH,

31:17.343 --> 31:19.977
TAKE A BOAT OUT ON THE CATAWBA
AND LEAVE MY CLIENT AT HOME.

31:19.979 --> 31:21.445
YOU'RE FREE TO LEAVE.

31:21.447 --> 31:23.347
MEANING YOU FOUND ZIP.

31:23.349 --> 31:25.082
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

31:25.084 --> 31:26.984
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

31:30.923 --> 31:31.955
Man: HERE THEY COME.

31:31.957 --> 31:33.957
Woman:
I HAVEN'T SEEN THEM YET.

31:36.028 --> 31:37.928
HEY, LINDA!

31:37.930 --> 31:40.430
REMEMBER ME
FROM ARTHUR FENTON'S HOUSE?

31:40.432 --> 31:41.598
[ GASPS ]

31:45.337 --> 31:48.305
IT'S NOT
WHAT YOU THINK.

31:48.307 --> 31:49.439
WHAT IS IT
THAT I THINK?

31:49.441 --> 31:51.308
THE HELL DID YOU JUST DO?

31:51.310 --> 31:54.278
WALK WITH ME.

31:54.280 --> 31:56.980
I THINK I JUST PLUGGED THE LEAK
IN THE CRIME LAB.

31:56.982 --> 31:59.483
YOU CAN EXPLAIN IT TO ME
DOWNTOWN.

32:03.989 --> 32:05.222
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

32:05.224 --> 32:06.690
COMING!

32:06.692 --> 32:09.626
YEAH, I'LL GET A-A ROUGH DRAFT
OUT TO YOU THIS AFTERNOON.

32:09.628 --> 32:11.845
HEY. LOOK.

32:11.846 --> 32:14.063
LOOKS LIKE THE STORY
MIGHT BE GOING NATIONAL.

32:14.066 --> 32:15.299
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

32:15.301 --> 32:17.134
A STORY
<i> IS</i> GOING NATIONAL.

32:17.136 --> 32:19.503
IT'S JUST NOT GONNA BE
ONE YOU WRITE.

32:19.505 --> 32:21.638
WHAT ARE YOU
GETTING AT, BEN?

32:21.640 --> 32:24.041
YOU PAID A LAB RAT
FOR TOM'S DNA RESULTS,

32:24.043 --> 32:25.709
THEN LEAKED THEM
TO THE PRESS.

32:25.711 --> 32:28.545
I'M PRETTY SURE
THAT'S ILLEGAL.

32:28.547 --> 32:30.514
YOU'D KNOW
BETTER THAN I WOULD.

32:30.516 --> 32:33.016
[ VEHICLES APPROACH ]

32:36.055 --> 32:37.421
WAIT.

32:37.423 --> 32:38.655
TIME'S UP.

32:38.657 --> 32:40.324
[ CAR DOORS CLOSING ]

32:40.326 --> 32:41.725
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

32:41.727 --> 32:43.360
IT'S OPEN.

32:44.697 --> 32:46.196
[ DOOR OPENS ]

32:46.198 --> 32:48.966
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

32:52.037 --> 32:53.036
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

32:53.038 --> 32:55.005
MR. FENTON.

33:08.721 --> 33:11.254
YOU REALLY HAVE A THING FOR ME,
DON'T YOU?

33:15.260 --> 33:18.028
YOU HERE TO GLOAT,
MR. CRAWFORD?

33:24.036 --> 33:27.037
YOU COMPROMISED MY LAB
AND MY CASES...

33:28.374 --> 33:30.173
...JUST TO GET BACK AT ME?

33:33.045 --> 33:35.112
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.
[ HANDCUFFS CLICKING ]

33:35.114 --> 33:38.315
ANYTHING YOU SAY
CAN AND WILL BE USED AGAINST YOU

33:38.317 --> 33:39.583
IN A COURT OF LAW.

33:39.585 --> 33:42.319
[ DOOR OPENS ]

33:42.321 --> 33:44.054
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

33:50.696 --> 33:53.230
WHAT WERE YOU DOING
IN THE WOODS?

33:53.232 --> 33:55.766
THIS AGAIN?

33:55.768 --> 33:58.235
ANSWER THE QUESTION.

33:58.237 --> 34:01.038
WHAT ARE YOU HIDING?

34:03.509 --> 34:05.242
YOU DON'T TRUST ME?

34:05.244 --> 34:07.328
NO, I DON'T.

34:07.329 --> 34:09.413
YOU HAVEN'T GIVEN ME
MUCH REASON TO IN A LONG TIME.

34:09.415 --> 34:11.281
I'VE TRIED
TO BE PATIENT.

34:11.283 --> 34:14.184
MY ENTIRE WORLD
HAS BEEN TURNED UPSIDE DOWN,

34:14.186 --> 34:15.685
AND I'VE STOOD BY YOU.

34:15.687 --> 34:18.221
I'VE DEFENDED YOU
TIME AND TIME AGAIN.

34:18.223 --> 34:21.224
TO WHO?
YOUR ELITIST FAMILY?

34:21.226 --> 34:22.793
THEY ALREADY THOUGHT
YOU MARRIED A LOSER.

34:22.795 --> 34:24.728
YEAH, WELL, I DIDN'T
WANT THEM TO BE RIGHT.

34:24.730 --> 34:27.397
IT'S ALWAYS ABOUT MONEY
FOR YOU --

34:27.399 --> 34:29.166
MONEY AND AND THE WAY THINGS
LOOK, KEEPING UP APPEARANCES!

34:29.168 --> 34:31.601
I WANTED SOMETHING MORE,
SOMETHING BETTER.

34:31.603 --> 34:33.170
ALL YOU WANT TO DO
IS COAST.

34:33.172 --> 34:35.205
NO, ALL I WANTED WAS YOU
AND THE GIRLS.

34:35.207 --> 34:37.174
AND I WANTED A MAN
WHO COULD KEEP UP WITH ME.

34:37.176 --> 34:38.675
WHAT THE HELL
DOES THAT MEAN?

34:38.677 --> 34:41.378
BETWEEN YOUR BROTHER AND YOUR
CLIENT, YOU GOT THAT COVERED.

34:41.380 --> 34:43.180
NOTHING HAPPENED
WITH SAM

34:43.182 --> 34:45.816
UNTIL I FOUND OUT ABOUT YOU AND
THAT WHORE ACROSS THE STREET.

34:45.818 --> 34:47.684
AT LEAST I OWN MY MISTAKES.

34:47.686 --> 34:49.519
YOU JUST LOOK FOR EXCU--
STOP BLAMING ME!

34:49.521 --> 34:51.555
YOUR BUSINESS FAILED.
YOU GAVE UP.

34:51.557 --> 34:54.291
IF IT WASN'T FOR ME, WE WOULDN'T
EVEN HAVE A ROOF OVER OUR HEADS.

34:54.293 --> 34:55.659
OUR KIDS
WOULD HAVE NOTHING.

34:55.661 --> 34:58.795
BUT WHEN I FIX A PROBLEM,
YOU RESENT ME FOR IT.

34:58.797 --> 35:00.730
I'M TIRED
OF TAKING CARE OF YOU.

35:00.732 --> 35:02.299
SO DON'T.
I DON'T WANT IT.

35:03.569 --> 35:06.770
TELL ME WHAT'S GOING ON,
OR I AM OUT OF HERE.

35:11.477 --> 35:13.743
THAT'S THE LAST ULTIMATUM
YOU GIVE ME.

35:13.745 --> 35:15.378
GO.

35:19.785 --> 35:22.119
NATALIE!

35:22.121 --> 35:23.370
ABBY!

35:23.371 --> 35:24.620
AND HERE'S
WHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN NEXT.

35:24.623 --> 35:26.590
YOU'RE GONNA RUN TO YOUR
BROTHER, CRY ON HIS SHOULDER.

35:26.592 --> 35:27.824
HE'LL GIVE YOU
A PLACE TO STAY

35:27.826 --> 35:29.392
AND TELL YOU
HOW MUCH BETTER OFF YOU ARE.

35:29.394 --> 35:31.595
BUT YOU AND I WILL AGREE
ON JOINT CUSTODY.

35:33.165 --> 35:34.631
GIRLS, LET'S GO.

35:34.633 --> 35:36.800
WELL,
WHY ARE YOU FIGHTING?

35:36.802 --> 35:37.801
WE'RE LEAVING.
WHY? WHAT'S GOING ON?

35:37.803 --> 35:38.836
I SAID LET'S GO.
DAD? DAD?

35:38.837 --> 35:39.870
Abby: I DON'T WANT TO GO.
GUYS.

35:39.872 --> 35:41.271
WHAT'S GOING ON?

35:41.273 --> 35:42.906
WHY AREN'T YOU TELLING ME
WHAT'S GOING ON?

35:42.908 --> 35:44.625
ABBY,
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY, HONEY.
HONEY.
DAD?

35:44.626 --> 35:46.343
I DON'T WANT TO GO!
[ SOBBING ]
Christy: WALK OUT THE DOOR.

35:46.345 --> 35:47.844
Ben: IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.
TAKE CARE OF YOUR SISTER.

35:47.846 --> 35:49.312
AND WE'RE GONNA
FIGURE THIS OUT.

35:49.314 --> 35:50.914
NATALIE,
PLEASE HELP ME.

35:50.915 --> 35:52.515
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.
IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.
I DON'T WANT TO GO!

35:52.518 --> 35:53.617
I KNOW, SWEETHEART.
HONEY.

35:53.619 --> 35:54.851
WE'RE -- WE'RE GONNA
FIGURE THIS OUT.

35:54.853 --> 35:57.387
I DON'T WANT TO GO!
WE HAVE TO STAY TOGETHER!

35:57.389 --> 35:58.588
IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.

35:58.590 --> 36:00.257
[ Sobbing ]
DON'T LET ME GO.

36:00.259 --> 36:02.225
ABBY, PLEASE COME
GET IN THE CAR.

36:02.227 --> 36:03.560
IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.

36:03.562 --> 36:04.661
Abby:
WHY ARE WE LEAVING?

36:04.663 --> 36:06.296
IT'S JUST TEMPORARY,
I PROMISE YOU.

36:06.298 --> 36:07.931
I DON'T WANT TO GO.

36:07.932 --> 36:09.565
[ Voice breaking ] GO WITH
YOUR MOM, JUST FOR TONIGHT.

36:09.568 --> 36:11.868
WE'RE GONNA FIGURE THIS OUT.
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY, ALL RIGHT?

36:11.870 --> 36:12.903
YOU JUST GOT TO BE STRONG.

36:12.905 --> 36:14.204
BUT WHAT ABOUT CHRISTMAS?

36:14.206 --> 36:16.206
WE'RE GONNA BE TOGETHER,
I PROMISE YOU.

36:22.881 --> 36:25.215
ABBY, COME GET IN THE CAR,
HONEY.

36:25.217 --> 36:26.816
ABBY.

36:26.818 --> 36:28.919
WHY ARE YOU
LEAVING DAD ALONE?!

36:28.921 --> 36:31.354
YOU DON'T CARE ABOUT ANYBODY
BUT YOURSELF!

36:31.356 --> 36:32.689
OKAY. OKAY, COME ON.
COME ON.

36:37.496 --> 36:40.363
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.

36:40.365 --> 36:41.631
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.

36:41.633 --> 36:43.767
[ PANTING ]

36:43.769 --> 36:46.803
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

36:46.805 --> 36:49.539
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

36:49.541 --> 36:50.907
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

37:06.725 --> 37:08.925
WHO THE HELL
EATS THESE THINGS?

37:08.927 --> 37:10.260
THEY'RE DISGUSTING.

37:10.262 --> 37:11.895
IS THIS WHY
YOU CALLED ME TO MEET?

37:11.897 --> 37:13.496
'CAUSE I GOT BETTER THINGS
TO DO.

37:13.498 --> 37:14.598
LIKE WHAT?

37:15.467 --> 37:17.400
THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT.
WHEN I CALL, YOU COME.

37:17.402 --> 37:18.902
NOW, WALK WITH ME.
I'M LATE FOR DINNER.

37:18.904 --> 37:20.971
[ SCOFFS ]
YOU'RE A JACKASS.
YOU DON'T HAVE TO LIKE ME.

37:20.973 --> 37:22.839
JUST DO WHAT I SAY,
AND I'LL KEEP YOU OUT OF PRISON.

37:22.841 --> 37:23.840
HOW'S THAT?

37:23.842 --> 37:25.659
IT WORKS.

37:25.660 --> 37:27.477
NOW, THE COPS WHO
PULLED YOU OVER WITHOUT CAUSE

37:27.479 --> 37:29.446
WERE NOT SENT BY CORNELL,
SO LET THAT GO.

37:29.448 --> 37:30.681
YOU SURE?

37:30.682 --> 37:31.915
I HAD A MEETING
AT INTERNAL AFFAIRS.

37:31.917 --> 37:33.950
A FEW COWBOYS WANTED
TO SHAKE YOUR TREE.

37:33.952 --> 37:38.622
AND, BY THE WAY, CORNELL'S
DAUGHTER, SHE<i> IS</i> A CRIMINAL.

37:38.624 --> 37:40.890
HER FATHER'S A SHRINK.
SHE STOLE HIS PRESCRIPTION PAD.

37:40.892 --> 37:43.260
SHE GOT PILLS FROM PHARMACIES
ALL OVER THE CITY

37:43.262 --> 37:44.761
AND GOT HIS LICENSE
SUSPENDED.

37:44.763 --> 37:46.329
WELL, SO, WHAT ARE YOU
TRYING TO SAY --

37:46.330 --> 37:47.896
CORNELL WAS RIGHT ABOUT HER,
SO SHE'S RIGHT ABOUT ME?

37:47.899 --> 37:49.466
DON'T START WITH
THE INNOCENCE AGAIN.

37:49.468 --> 37:51.935
NO, MAN.
I'M GUILTY...OF PLENTY.

37:51.937 --> 37:54.404
JUST NOT
WHAT I WAS ACCUSED OF.

37:54.406 --> 37:58.408
I'VE BEEN HARASSED AND YELLED AT
AND SMEARED AND TORTURED.

37:58.410 --> 37:59.876
I'M DONE
GETTING PUSHED AROUND.

37:59.878 --> 38:00.777
GOOD.

38:00.779 --> 38:02.779
IT'S ABOUT DAMN TIME.

38:02.781 --> 38:04.914
I'LL CALL YOU.

38:08.020 --> 38:10.387
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

38:14.826 --> 38:16.893
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

38:18.864 --> 38:20.330
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

38:24.036 --> 38:26.336
I PACKED UP SOME THINGS,
AND I WANT THE GIRLS

38:26.338 --> 38:28.305
TO HAVE THEIR GIFTS
FIRST THING TOMORROW.

38:28.307 --> 38:29.806
I'LL PUT THEM
UNDER THE TREE.

38:29.808 --> 38:33.643
CALLING THE COPS ON ME
WAS PRETTY LOW.

38:36.348 --> 38:39.949
WHEN MY SISTER GETS UPSET,
I TRY TO FIX IT.

38:39.951 --> 38:43.453
SHE SHARED HER SUSPICIONS
WITH ME, AND I TOLD THE POLICE.

38:43.455 --> 38:46.790
ANY HONEST CITIZEN WOULD'VE
DONE THE SAME THING, BEN.

38:46.792 --> 38:48.858
YOU NEED TO GET
A GOOD LAWYER.

38:48.860 --> 38:51.394
I HAVE ONE.

38:51.396 --> 38:52.996
YOU KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THAT?

38:55.367 --> 38:57.000
GOOD NIGHT.

39:02.941 --> 39:04.874
[ RAIN FALLING ]

39:07.612 --> 39:09.679
[ SWITCH CLICKING ]

39:20.959 --> 39:22.926
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

39:35.407 --> 39:37.707
DON'T YOU EVER QUIT?

39:39.745 --> 39:43.012
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO
GO THROUGH MY LAWYER.

39:43.014 --> 39:45.815
WOULD YOU LIKE
TO GIVE HIM A CALL?

39:54.726 --> 39:57.794
IT'S CHRISTMAS EVE.

39:57.796 --> 40:00.029
WHERE'S YOUR FAMILY?

40:00.031 --> 40:02.966
WHERE'S YOURS?

40:02.968 --> 40:04.934
[ LIQUID POURING ]

40:07.639 --> 40:12.842
YOU HAVE A LOT OF PEOPLE THAT
CARE ABOUT YOU, MR. CRAWFORD.

40:12.844 --> 40:14.911
YOUR KIDS
ARE WELL-BEHAVED...

40:14.913 --> 40:17.981
MOST OF THE TIME.

40:17.983 --> 40:20.650
IT WOULD BE A SHAME
TO LOSE THAT.

40:20.652 --> 40:23.853
YOU WOULD KNOW.

40:23.855 --> 40:27.757
MY DAUGHTER HAD A CHOICE.
SHE CHOSE JAIL.

40:30.162 --> 40:31.928
I'M NOT GONNA
SAY IT AGAIN.

40:31.930 --> 40:33.797
WHAT?

40:33.799 --> 40:37.467
THAT YOU DIDN'T KILL
TOM MURPHY?

40:37.469 --> 40:39.836
HOW CAN YOU BE SO SURE?

40:39.838 --> 40:43.206
BECAUSE I KNOW
MY CHARACTER.

40:43.208 --> 40:44.941
I'M NOT VIOLENT.

40:44.943 --> 40:46.943
REALLY?

40:46.944 --> 40:48.944
I WITNESSED SEVERAL INSTANCES
OF YOUR VIOLENCE --

40:48.947 --> 40:50.580
WITH YOUR FRIEND DAVE,

40:50.582 --> 40:53.917
THE VIDEO FOOTAGE OF THE BOY
THAT YOU THREATENED TO KILL.

40:53.919 --> 40:56.519
[ SIGHS ]

40:56.521 --> 41:00.123
SO YOU DIDN'T SEE JESS MURPHY
THE NIGHT TOM DIED?
NOPE.

41:00.125 --> 41:01.958
AND YOU DIDN'T SEE TOM?

41:01.960 --> 41:04.694
AND YOU RODE HOME ALONE
IN A TAXI, CORRECT?

41:04.696 --> 41:06.896
WE'VE BEEN THROUGH
ALL THIS.

41:06.898 --> 41:08.865
I TRACKED DOWN THE DRIVER,

41:08.867 --> 41:12.869
AND WE GOT THE SURVEILLANCE
FOOTAGE OF HIS CAB.

41:19.144 --> 41:21.478
I ALREADY TOLD YOU
I WAS DRUNK.

41:21.480 --> 41:23.246
KEEP WATCHING.

41:38.129 --> 41:42.131
SO YOU DON'T REMEMBER GOING
TO JESS MURPHY'S THAT NIGHT?

41:42.133 --> 41:47.070
EITHER YOU'RE LYING
OR YOU HAD A BLACKOUT,

41:47.072 --> 41:51.641
WHICH MEANS YOU'RE CAPABLE
OF JUST ABOUT ANYTHING.

42:04.756 --> 42:07.857
MERRY CHRISTMAS,
MR. CRAWFORD.

42:07.859 --> 42:10.026
[ DOOR OPENS ]

42:10.028 --> 42:11.160
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
